{"tid":91849,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[假難民]印度客今起需預辦入境登記","createTime":"2017-01-23T06:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T00:29:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"424236865da1d680a2180895abc5c540522cf360","tid":91849,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Yx95CL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FYx95CL.jpg&h=7631f3b0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】假難民肆虐本港，而印度國民可免簽證訪港十四天的待遇，成部分當地假難民濫用來港「舉手」提出免遣返聲請的途徑。 <br />\n<br />\n截至去年底，尚待審核免遣返聲請有九千九百八十一宗，最大來源國印度佔積壓個案兩成。入境處的「印度國民預辦入境登記」措施今日（23日）正式實施，今日起除某些類別人士獲豁免外，印度國民須預先網上申請及成功辦妥預辦入境登記，才可續享免簽來港旅遊或過境不超過十四天的待遇。「香港政府一站通」網頁上的「印度國民預辦入境登記」平台已在去年十二月十九日開放。 <br />\n<br />\n預辦入境登記是免費的措施，系統收到所需資料後會即時顯示結果，成功辦妥登記者須列印出相關的通知書，連同用以登記的指定有效印度護照，作為登上來港運輸工具及辦理入境檢查手續之用。"},{"pid":"13ac8ce79e1576aa2724d07586bff3127949ff1a","tid":91849,"uid":54778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdafa3b4a75c19710cd95f5a024a7d9e2a8c767","tid":91849,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:37:52.000Z","msg":"終於阿差冇14日免簽入港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣都唔明點解俾阿差免簽入港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19198018d9bd8e4c77a54dc02ed6574724815f39","tid":91849,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7466122e2731f99ac8e5f3d03416d2e7c974538","tid":91849,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no